            <title>[LU-11049] lgss-sk: incorrect &apos;fsname&apos; and &apos;nodemap&apos; string handling</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11049</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;lgss_sk does not properly handle &apos;fsname&apos; and &apos;nodemap&apos; strings passed by user. It forgets to add the null byte at the end.&lt;br/&gt;
I will push a patch to address this issue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Cheers,&lt;br/&gt;
Sebastien.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
